high_descs: Make a right to walk to the bed.
Close and pick up the laptop on the bed.
Make a left and walk around the bed to the nightstand on the left of the bed.
Turn on the lamp on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a laptop on the bed to look at under a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the end of the bed.
Close the lid of the laptop on the bed and pick it up.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the nightstand.
Turn on the light of the small lamp that is on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Examine a closed laptop in the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the bed.
Close the laptop and pick it up.
Turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the nightstand.
Turn on the light on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a laptop by lamp light?
